document_title: Erectile dysfunction in women: Causes, symptoms and ways to improve
subsection_name: yeu-sinh-ly-o-nu.json_1_What is erectile dysfunction in women?
subsection_content:
Erectile dysfunction in women is a condition of decreased sexual desire or no longer interested in sex. It can occur at any age, including women in their prime, but the most common group is still preteen women. menopause – menopause. (2)
Female physiological weakness makes women feel afraid and want to avoid being close to their husbands, which over time affects family happiness.
